    "description": "Solara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions has an exciting opening for a Surgeon at our Meerut office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Solara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions:\nSolara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Solara Active Pharma Ventures Solutions!",
